         [\fB\-o\fP \fI[<.xvg>]\fP] [\fB\-odg\fP \fI[<.xvg>]\fP] [\fB\-or\fP \fI[<.xvg>]\fP] [\fB\-oa\fP \fI[<.xvg>]\fP]
